description: Redevelopment of 44-52 High Street comprising construction of a nine-storey building with retail at ground floor and 61 flats above; and development 26a-34 High Street to provide 40 residential units by conversion of the public house use at ground level and the offices and ancillary residential accommodation on the first and second floors and construction of two additional floors; together with the provision of rear servicing to both sites from Cecil Road.
